high_descs: turn around and walk over to the oven
grab the butter knife to the right of the oven on the kitchen counter
turn around and walk over to the kitchen stove
place the butter knife in the pan on the back right burner on the stove
pick up the pan with the butter knife in it
turn around and walk to the coffee maker on the table to the left
place the pan down on the table in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a butter knife in it on the table in front of the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room to the black oven.
Take the knife from the counter on the right of the oven.
Turn around, go across the room to the white oven.
Put the knife in the pot on the right back burner on the stove top.
Take the pan from the right back burner on the stop top.
Turn around, go to the white table facing its long side.
Put the pot in front of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the oven.
Pick up the knife that's to the right of the oven.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the stove then take a step to your right.
Put the knife in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the middle of the table on your left and then turn left to face it.
Put the pan on the table near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, then go left, then go straight, to the oven.
Pick up the knife on the counter, to the right of the oven and in front of the salt.
Turn left, then turn left, then go straight toward the stove, then turn right, then turn to face the stove.
Put the knife in the rightmost pot on the stove.
Pick up the rightmost pot on the stove.
Turn left, then turn left, then turn left again to face the coffee maker on the table.
Place the pot on the table, in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on the table.
